Class JsonApiProvider<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.explorviz.discovery.server.providers.JsonApiProvider<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - - To-be (de-) serialized type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyReader<T>, javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyWriter<T>

    @Provider
 @Produces(value="application/vnd.api+json")
 @Consumes(value="application/vnd.api+json")
public class JsonApiProvider<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyReader<T>, javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyWriter<T>
    This provider enables the automatic serialization and deserialization for objects of types Agent and Procezz.
